@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_stffsd(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (0.90 - wp.abs(wp.exp(v0 + 0.28)))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.sin((v0 + 0.90 * tmp + 0.79)))
    v2 = tmp
    v2 = (0.69 * wp.exp(0.06))
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.cos((v0 + 0.36 + v2 + 0.36)))
    v0 = (((tmp + 0.16 / v2 + 0.38) * (tmp + 0.64 + tmp + 0.21)) - ((v2 + 0.16 / tmp + 0.28) * v0))
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.exp(v1 + 0.83)) * wp.exp(v2))
    data[tid] = v0
